		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div data-pf-type="Body" class="sc-pRgDJ fzXWJx pf-221f955a"><div data-pf-type="Layout" class="pf-1d99221f"><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-39f0dbc7" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-0bd3015f pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-f12ed9bb" data-pf-type="Column"><h1 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-994df12e"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-ba9d994d">Shipping & Returns</span></h1></div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-b70f5dce pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-e94f52cd" data-pf-type="Column"><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC jHjrlE pf-e83015cc"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-6ff46372 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-1d9b00e2 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="dc1d9b00-e24c-4e2d-828b-c8b17e8cb3f9" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="true" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position fa fa-minus"></i>When does my chocolate ship?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-8cb3f91d accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="dc1d9b00-e24c-4e2d-828b-c8b17e8cb3f9" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: block;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-00e24c5e"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-80d57745"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Store Purchases<br></span>Orders ship on business days Monday thru Thursday to prevent melt. We monitor weather and transit time to determine when we can ship, to ensure the chocolate arrives to you safely. If temperatures are too hot we reserve the right to hold your order until it is cooler.<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Club Subscribers<br></span>Bar & Cocoa subscriptions ship early in the second week of every month. Every shipment should arrive by the end of the same week. The cut off date is the 6th of each month. (But chat us up, we can often accommodate a few late orders!)<br><br><span style="font-style: italic;">Examples&nbsp;</span><br>Subscription ordered: January 27th<br>First box shipped: Second Monday or Tuesday of February<br><br>Subscription ordered:&nbsp;February 5th<br>First box shipped:&nbsp;Second Monday or Tuesday of March</span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-63726bb9 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-4c5e2d42 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="e24c5e2d-428b-48b1-be8c-b3f91d42966f" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position fa fa-plus"></i>How do you package & ship the chocolate?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-f91d4296 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="e24c5e2d-428b-48b1-be8c-b3f91d42966f" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-2d428bc8"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-f87e0020">We utilize <span style="font-weight: bold;">minimal eco-friendly packaging to ship each order</span>. In the warmer months, we add ice and insulation to ensure your chocolate arrives in perfect condition. Our ice packs are 100% biodegradable. It helps if you keep an eye out on delivery days and bring in your package as soon as possible. We reserve the right to hold your order if temperature is above 100F.<br><br>We use USPS for most standard 3-5 day shipments and Fedex Express for priority 2 Day shipments for continental US orders. We ship anywhere almost anywhere in the world and shipping for international orders is calculated at checkout..&nbsp;<br><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Bar & Cocoa is not responsible for delays resulting from mishandling by the shipping carrier.&nbsp;We reserve the right to change shipping methods at any time without notice.</span></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-6bb9e830 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-8bc8b17e accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="428bc8b1-7e8c-43f9-9d42-966ff463726b" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position fa fa-plus"></i>How can I track my order?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-42966ff4 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="428bc8b1-7e8c-43f9-9d42-966ff463726b" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-b17e8cb3"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-b2dc1d9b">Tracking numbers are emailed to you upon shipment. When in doubt, check your email or your store account. If you can't find it, we can resend it to you. Contact us using the form below or email <a href="mailto:info@barandcocoa.com">info@barandcocoa.com</a><br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-0403419f" data-pf-type="Column"><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC jHjrlE pf-7663e36f"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-53c813c5 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-e1bb4c13 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="d46c06e5-3d31-486c-82a7-b5a31255795f" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="true" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position fa fa-minus"></i>What About International Shipping?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-71914224 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="d46c06e5-3d31-486c-82a7-b5a31255795f" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: block;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-eb5ecf1a"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-0fbdeb5e">We love shipping chocolate all around the world. Because of the costs associated with shipping internationally, all <span style="font-weight: bold;">international orders are final sale</span>. Please review your country's international custom and duties as we are not responsible for the payment of those fees. The club subscription is only available in the United States at this time.<br><br>We ship to over 220 countries usually via DHL Express. Shipping cost is dynamic, and calculated at checkout based on the total weight.</span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-13c56cc1 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-4c130921 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="6c06e53d-31a8-4c42-a7b5-a31255795f63" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position fa fa-plus"></i>My order was lost or damaged during delivery.</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-4c51ca8e accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="6c06e53d-31a8-4c42-a7b5-a31255795f63" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-3940a1d5"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-f27d3940">Please email us at <a href="mailto:info@barandcocoa.com">info@barandcocoa.com</a> with your order number and a detailed account of your issue, and we will do our best to find a solution.<br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-6cc17663 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper">